# Leapfrog Connect LMS — Setup Guide

## Project Structure

```
lms_project/
├── backend/          ← Django + DRF + JWT
│   ├── api/          ← All models, views, serializers, urls
│   ├── core/         ← settings.py, core/urls.py
│   ├── manage.py
│   └── requirements.txt
└── lms-frontend/     ← React + Vite + Tailwind
    └── src/
        ├── pages/
        ├── components/
        ├── layout/
        ├── services/
        └── context/
```

---

## Backend Setup

```bash
cd backend

# 1. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 2. Make and run migrations
python manage.py makemigrations
python manage.py migrate

# 3. Create superuser (already done: kapil@gmail.com / kapil123)
python manage.py createsuperuser

# 4. Seed demo courses, lessons, quizzes and jobs
# Just call the endpoint once after starting the server:
# POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/seed/

# 5. Run server
python manage.py runserver
```

---

## Frontend Setup

```bash
cd lms-frontend

# 1. Install dependencies
npm install

# 2. Start dev server
npm run dev
```

---

## First Run Checklist

1. Start Django: `python manage.py runserver`
2. Seed data: `POST http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/seed/` (use Postman or browser)
3. Start React: `npm run dev`
4. Open browser: `http://localhost:5173`
5. Login: `kapil@gmail.com` / `kapil123`

---

## Key API Endpoints

| Method | URL                              | Auth | Description                     |
| ------ | -------------------------------- | ---- | ------------------------------- |
| POST   | /api/token/                      | ❌   | Login (get JWT)                 |
| POST   | /api/register/                   | ❌   | Register                        |
| GET    | /api/courses/                    | ❌   | List all courses                |
| GET    | /api/courses/:id/                | ❌   | Course detail + lessons         |
| POST   | /api/enroll/                     | ✅   | Enroll in course                |
| GET    | /api/my-courses/                 | ✅   | My enrolled courses             |
| POST   | /api/complete-lesson/            | ✅   | Mark lesson done                |
| GET    | /api/lesson-progress/:course_id/ | ✅   | Get completed lessons           |
| GET    | /api/quiz/:course_id/            | ✅   | Get quiz (must complete course) |
| POST   | /api/quiz/:quiz_id/submit/       | ✅   | Submit quiz answers             |
| GET    | /api/my-certificates/            | ✅   | My earned certificates          |
| GET    | /api/jobs/                       | ❌   | List jobs                       |
| POST   | /api/apply/                      | ✅   | Apply for a job                 |
| GET    | /api/my-applications/            | ✅   | My job applications             |
| GET    | /api/profile/                    | ✅   | Get profile                     |
| PUT    | /api/update-profile/             | ✅   | Update profile                  |
| GET    | /api/dashboard-stats/            | ✅   | Dashboard stats                 |
| POST   | /api/seed/                       | ❌   | Seed demo data                  |

